<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q9_v1" title="Q9_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Una persona fue a una charcutería y compró tres tipos de queso, todos vendidos por kilogramo. Compró tres cuartos de kilo de queso mantecoso, un kilo y medio de queso gauda y medio kilo de queso parmesano.</p>
    <p>Los precios por kilogramo son los siguientes: queso gauda: $5600 el kilogramo; queso parmesano: $8900 el kilogramo; queso mantecoso: $4200 el kilogramo.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el monto total que pagó por los quesos?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión asigna mal los precios. En esta opción, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, pero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> corresponde al queso mantecoso, cuyo precio es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. También <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, pero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> corresponde al queso gauda, cuyo precio es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. La expresión correcta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3150</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4450</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La expresión multiplica cada cantidad por el precio del queso correspondiente: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> para el mantecoso, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> para el gauda y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> para el parmesano. Al calcular, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3150</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4450</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Las cantidades no coinciden con la compra del enunciado. La persona compró <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> de queso gauda y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> de queso parmesano, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,2</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> ni <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,2</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso esta expresión representa otra compra: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3150</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6720</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1780</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;650</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que no corresponde al monto total pedido.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La cantidad de queso mantecoso es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2,75</m:mn><m:mi>kg</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso el primer producto de esta opción no representa la compra descrita. Esta expresión calcula <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;550</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4450</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24&#160;400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, mientras que el monto correcto se obtiene con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar la cantidad de cada queso</strong></p>
            <p>Queso mantecoso: tres cuartos de kilo, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> kg.</p>
            <p>Queso gauda: un kilo y medio, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> kg.</p>
            <p>Queso parmesano: medio kilo, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> kg.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Asociar cada cantidad con su precio por kilogramo</strong></p>
            <p>Mantecoso: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Gauda: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Parmesano: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Escribir la expresión del monto total</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular cada producto</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3150</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>5600</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>8900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Sumar los tres valores</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3150</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4450</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión que representa correctamente el monto total pagado es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>